# 🚀 Main Features

## 1. High-Performance Next.js Architecture

Built with **Next.js Server-Side Rendering (SSR)** to ensure blazing-fast page loading, improved SEO, and better user experience.

## 2. Unlimited Website Pages & Blog Posts

Create and manage unlimited pages, landing pages, service pages, and blog posts without any restrictions.

## 3. Visual Page Builder

Easily build and customize pages using a flexible page builder with reusable content blocks and dynamic layouts.

## 4. 50+ Ready-to-Use Sections

Choose from over **50 professionally designed sections and components** to quickly create stunning pages.

## 5. Dynamic Menu Management

Create, edit, organize, and manage navigation menus with support for multi-level menu structures.

## 6. Advanced Footer Editor

Fully customize website footer content, links, contact information, and branding elements.

## 7. Analytics & Marketing Integrations

Built-in support for:

* Google Tag Manager (GTM)
* Google Analytics 4 (GA4)
* Facebook Pixel (FBP)
* Facebook Conversion API (CAPI)

Track visitors, conversions, and marketing performance effortlessly.

## 8. SEO Optimized

Comes with SEO-friendly architecture including:

* Dynamic metadata management
* Open Graph support
* SSR optimization
* Search engine indexing improvements

## 9. Mobile Responsive Design

Fully responsive across desktops, tablets, and mobile devices with optimized layouts for every screen size.

## 10. Media Library Management

Upload, organize, and manage images, videos, documents, and other media assets from a centralized media library.

## 11. Secure Authentication System

Comprehensive user authentication and verification system with session management and security controls.

## 12. Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

Advanced permission management system for teams, administrators, editors, and custom user roles.

## 13. Production Ready

Built for scalability, security, and high-performance deployment environments.

